{"tid":1906690,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［民間記者會］一日一界別：都市規劃；仲差至少800人！！！","createTime":"2020-03-02T05:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T03:56:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c124df22f8219b3e04484da71c8be97c20256c1b","tid":1906690,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T05:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gQcwDUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgQcwDUK.png&h=4699f30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《一日一界別 &mdash; 建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界功能界別》<br />\n截至2019年建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界功能界別的登記選民人數為8026人。距離光復此界別至少尚欠800個人票。<br />\n界別中屬都市規劃專業的選民包括所有根據《規劃師註冊條例》（第 418 章）註冊的專業規劃師或有權在香港規劃師學會的大會上表決的該會會員。<br />\n其餘三個同屬此界別的專業&mdash;&mdash;建築、都市規劃、園境，有關選民資格請參閱之前及之後的帖文。<br />\n=====================<br />\n用填表機一分鐘搞掂：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=03b241fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n手動填表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-41%28C%29.pdf&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=6ad029da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-41(C).pdf</a><br />\n網上交表：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Findex.jsp&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=c45e0236\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp</a><br />\n其他相關資料：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/aspl_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Faspl_c.pdf&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=1692b589\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/aspl_c.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/gn-full_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fgn%2Fgn-full_c.pdf&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=59e9010c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/gn/gn-full_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hkercpc/?__tn__=%2Cg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhkercpc%2F%3F__tn__%3D%252Cg&d=cG87S%2FC0TFnLRhO0hL0igSLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=cad43f88\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hkercpc/?__tn__=%2Cg</a>"},{"pid":"6deafb3a8c3e37fa19672afc2de96723d7f12258","tid":1906690,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:10:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838f0b171a4506ed7ec4473d5c113f4cb0bc9e4c","tid":1906690,"uid":51924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"150e8798c0ff515f01275ce937056b2ac7326f79","tid":1906690,"uid":110043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1000a20a1ff7e0c89f560be028f4e531824ea801","tid":1906690,"uid":95452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:51:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55e35d0899b33b29b3cf00b82b83fa34789ec0ac","tid":1906690,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:06:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2500ff3d3e4a4a3edd53e214113076836cccf368","tid":1906690,"uid":284590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T14:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" clas